dct_description_sm: Engraved and printed by the U.S. Geological Survey.
Includes inset location map and bar scales in miles and "kilometres"
Shows villages, ruins, drainage, canal, roads and trails, borders, range lights, Panama Railroad, ICC facilities (sanitarium, quarry, san pit), continental divide, French canal
